SUMMARY:Salsa at Politan  Row at the Colony Square
DESCRIPTION:🎉💃 Salsa & Bachata Sundays at Politan Row! 🕺🎶 at the Colony Square. \n🔥 Every 3rd Sunday of the Month 🔥\n📍 Politan Row at Colony Square – Atlanta\, GA \nGet ready to spice up your Sunday with a sizzling mix of salsa and bachata\, delicious food\, and unbeatable vibes! \n🎓 Courtesy Salsa/Bachata Class\n🕒 3:00 – 4:00 PM\n👨‍🏫 Taught by the incredible Alfredo Piceno \n🎧 Party with DJ Italiano\n🕔 4:00 – 7:00 PM \n🎵 Latin rhythms to keep you on the floor all afternoon! \n🌮 Enjoy diverse global cuisine\, a full bar\, a beautiful dance floor\, and a welcoming community of dancers. Whether you’re new to the scene or a seasoned pro\, this is your Sunday spot! \n✅ Free Cover | 💃 All Levels Welcome | 🥂 Great Vibes Only \n🎉 Hosted by Salsambo – Bringing the heat to ATL!\n📅 Mark your calendars and don’t miss a beat – see you on the dance floor! \n#SalsaSundays #BachataLovers #PolitanRowATL #Salsambo #LatinDanceAtlanta #DanceAndDine #SalsaWithAlfredo #DJItalianoVibes #AtlantaDanceScene
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-at-politan-row-at-the-colony-square/2026-03-15/
LOCATION:Politan Row at Colony Square\, Colony Square\, Atlanta\, GA\, United States
CATEGORIES:Atlanta
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/508119131_10238326970614085_691623826266637266_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
