SUMMARY:Sunday Dance Matinee Cuban Edition - March
DESCRIPTION:🎉AGUAAAAAAA‼️Don’t miss our next SUNDAY DANCE MATINEE: Cuban Edition🕺💃🏽💥FREE ENTRANCE💥 \n🕛 SUNDAY\, MARCH 15\nDANCE MATINEE from 3p.m. to 8p.m.\, so arrive early to get the most of your dance fix! \n🎧Guest DJ Walter Soto will be playing the best of Salsa\, Timba\, Bachata\, and Reparto (Cuban Reggaetón) 🎶🎵 \n🕛Cuban Son class @ 3p.m. with Jarryd Randolph from Casino Revó Dance \n📍ADDRESS: 809 Lounge Restaurant & Grill\, 3710 W Waters Ave\, Tampa\, FL 33614 \n🎉809 Lounge Restaurant & Grill offers a wide selection of food\, beer\, and cocktails available for purchase. We appreciate your SUPPORT BY LEAVING ALL YOUR PERSONAL BEVERAGES AT HOME. By supporting dance venues\, we can keep them open for years to come so we can enjoy dancing. 😁 \nTHANK YOU for supporting the venue and the opportunity to bring this event to you monthly. \nBrought to you by Dame Salsa Cubana\, Casino Revó\, & DJ Mazi
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/sunday-dance-matinee-cuban-edition-march/
LOCATION:809 Lounge Restaurant & Grill\, 3710 W Waters Ave\, Tampa\, FL\, 33614\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tampa
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/636731791_122122711539136986_678128405278627992_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
