SUMMARY:MUÉVETE Bachata Sundays
DESCRIPTION:✨NEW✨\n💜MUÉVETE💜 \nBACHATA SUNDAYS \n😎 Every Sunday \n👯‍♀️ 4pm Beginner Class\n👯‍♀️ 5pm Intermediate Class\n🎶 6pm-9pm SOCIAL PARTY \nYour Maetros & Hosts:\n💃 @minxhafon\n🕺 @kendrickjrodriguez \nFREE ENTRY\nwith any dance class purchase* \n*dance class must be from the same week \nPARTY ONLY\n$10 Pre-paid\n$15 on the day \nDANCE CLASSES\n$29.90 x1 casual class\n$54.90 x2 casual classes \nTerm packages also available 👀 \n🎉 Book your party tix here:\nhttps://bit.ly/muevetebachata \n🎉 Book your dance class here:\nhttps://bit.ly/mbassycasual \n🕺🏽Book your term rego here:\nhttps://bit.ly/danceclasstermrego \nFinish your week with Muévete 💜✨
