SUMMARY:Latin Sunday Sessions
DESCRIPTION:Every weekend we turn Green Square plaza into an open dance space. \nOur hosts alternate each weekend to put on one of the best Latin nights in Sydney. Dance the night away to salsa\, bachata with a touch of merengue and reggaeton. \nWe always aim to do a complete outdoor setup but if the weather isn’t in our favour we bring it inside \nVamos a prenderle fuego a la pista de baile!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/latin-sunday-sessions-2/2026-03-15/
