SUMMARY:Salsa & Bachata Boat Parties! Dance\, Sip\, Have a blast! DJ Keoke on the mix
DESCRIPTION:Everyone! You all are invited to dance Salsa\, Bachata Merengue Cumbia on the water! Drinks\, potluck\, sunset\, and hot DJ sets! All welcome.\n\n\nHappy Sunday Funday all! – Let’s Salsa Bachata Boat Party!\n  \nThe Salsa Bachata Boat Party Line up of 2026 Is Here! \n🚨Don’t miss your chance to vibe with us on the water! 🚢💃🏻🕺🏻 \n🎟️ Tickets: Early Bird $60/person. \n📲 Group of 6 or more discounts: 832-413-2623 \n📍 South Shore Harbour Resort 2500 S. Shore Blvd\, League City\, TX \n🕠 Boarding: 5:30p. Don’t be late! \n🛳️ Sailing: 6–9p. 3 Hour Boat ride. \n🎧 DJ Felipe & Keoke on the mix! We alternate DJ’s \n  \n🔥 UPCOMING PARTIES \n📅 Nov 16\, 2025 Friendsgiving Party Boat (5 spots left) \n📅 Feb 15\, 2026 Love Boat for Singles & Couples \n📅 Mar 15\, 2026 Spring Celebration Boat \n📅 Apr 19th\, 2026 Bad Bunny Party Boat \n📅 May 3rd\, 2026 Cinco De Mayo \n📅 May 24th\, 2026 Memorial Day Weekend \n📅 Jun 14th\, 2026 LDF Anniversary Boat \n📅 Jul 5th\, 2026 Independence Day Boat. Red\, White & Blue Theme \n📅 Aug 9th\, 2026 White Linen Party Boat \n📅 Sep 6th\, 2026 Labor Day Weekend Boat \n📅 Sep 27th\, 2026 Fall Celebration Party Boat \n📅 Oct 25th\, 2026 Halloween Bash Party Boat \n  \n💥 No dance partner or experience needed! \nGet your tickets NOW! \nGet ready to relax and chill on a sunday afternoon the Latin way – on the water\, with music\, dancing\, and high energy vibes! 🛥️💃🏻🕺🏻 \n  \n  \n🚨 TICKET INFO (All-Inclusive!)\n🎟️ Includes: \n\nMini Dance ice-breaker.\n3-hour boat ride\nOpen bar (beer\, wine\, tequila\, vodka & mixers – top shelf)\nSnacks & potluck\nDJ\, dancing\, pictures & more!\n\n  \n💸 Pricing: \n\n🎉 Early Bird : $60/person\n🚨 Sunday Walk-ins: $75/person – Text 832-413-2623 first to check availability\nGroup discount for 6 or more available. Text us.\n\n📲 To reserve your spot: Buy on Eventbrite or text “Boat” to 832-413-2623 with your name & guest names. \nMax 75 spots per boat party only! Walk-ins are not recommended. \n  \n⏰ SCHEDULE\n\nBoarding starts: 5:30 PM (Don’t be late!)\nDeparture: 6 PM sharp\nReturn: 9 PM\n\n  \n📍 LOCATION \nHouston Party Boats @ South Shore Harbour Pier. \n2500 S. Shore Blvd\, League City\, TX 77573 \n(Park at the pier – not in the hotel garage) \n  \n🥳 CELEBRATE WITH US!\nNo partner needed. Come solo\, bring a date\, or rally your friends! Celebrating a birthday? We will do a special shotout. 🎂 \n  \n☀️ WHAT TO BRING\n\nYour fave beer/wine (optional)\nSunglasses\, good vibes\nPotluck sides or snacks welcome\nBirthday cake? Yes! (Just not ice cream)\nBig smiles.\n\n  \n🌦️ WEATHER POLICY\nBoat is covered & cozy! Rain? We’ve got side covers. Hot? The breeze + fans keep it cool. Cold? We’ve got heaters. \nIf extreme rainy weather cancels the cruise\, you’ll get a full refund or credit towards the next boat party upon your choice. No problem. \n  \n💬 QUESTIONS? TEXT ME!\nChristian Franco | Latin Dance Factory \n📱 832-413-2623 (Se habla Español) \n📅 Need help with Salsa and Bachata turns? Dance Calendar: linktr.ee/latindancefactory \n📸 Instagram: @latindancefactory \n  \n#partieseveryday #salsaboat #birthdaybash #sundayfunday #houstonboatparty #houstonevents #djkeoke #salsa #bachata #cumbia #merengue #houstonparty #latinmusic
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-bachata-boat-parties-dance-sip-have-a-blast-dj-keoke-on-the-mix/2026-03-15/
LOCATION:Houston Party Boats\, 2500 South Shore Boulevard\, League City\, TX 77573\, League City\, TX\, 77573\, US
CATEGORIES:Houston
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/299946_image.png
END:VEVENT
